title: Recall Notification Report 115-2015 (Boneless Beef Tender Tips)
summary: WASHINGTON, Aug. 27, 2015 Swanson Meats, a Minneapolis, Minn., establishment, is recalling approximately 20,063 pounds of beef products due to misbranding, the U.S. Department of Agricultures Food Safety and Inspection Service (FSIS) announced today.
